outputs.output_descr: The BRA/00/009 project aims to develop and implement: (1) management tools, (2) rules and procedures for carrying out control actions of the federal environmental agency (IBAMA), for the preservation and conservation of Brazilian Ecosystems, (3 ) Control System, Management, Archiving and Availability of documents and technical-scientific information.
